posting_body: ['Welcome to Miro', 'Miro reflects the dynamic, multi-faceted character of contemporary life.', 'Start your day with a boost of energy at the fitness center, hone in on work from the comfortable co-working lounges, and wrap up the evening soaking up tranquility from the rooftop sky deck.', 'Come home to the perfect blend of easy relaxation, bold design, and quality finishes.', 'Live beyond your expectations.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Fire Pit', 'Controlled Access', 'Private Game Lounge', 'Exclusive Rooftop Demonstration Kitchen', 'Capacious Closets', 'EV Charging Stations', 'Yoga Studio', 'Private Co-Working Spaces', 'Expansive Balconies', 'Fitness Center', 'Private Screening Room', 'Bike Storage', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
